title: How has the proportion of obese 10-11 year old children changed over time?
analysis_commentary: One in three children in year 6 were overweight or obese in 2013/14 with 33.5%. The proportion of year 6 children who are obese has increased by approx. 1.6% during this time period. The proportion who are overweight or underweight has remained stable over this time period.
